{"tid":1904782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民自救]搵到YouTube推薦/熱門大量殘字影片嘅原因","createTime":"2020-02-29T19:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T06:55:09.000Z","uid":57911,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9c58c0b45df805548d28a24a5971bbefb248dd","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T19:51:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟今日開無痕睇YouTube<br />\n咁啱第一個推薦就係講VPN網速講翻牆就入去睇下<br />\n俾我發現到個主持人介紹背景速度係用香港嘅網絡嚟試<br />\n原因又快又順流量又夠大<br />\n<br />\n咁問題就嚟<br />\n如果九成支那人都係用香港VPN嚟睇YouTube<br />\n咁咪會洗走晒本地啲熱門<br />\n久而久之香港YouTube淨係會推薦埋啲強國片播強國app廣告<br />\n亦都縮窄香港YouTuber上推薦頁嘅機會<br />\n你一冇登入ac一冇撳走啲垃圾片(不感興趣)<br />\n就會瘋狂彈啲支那片出嚟<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，大家幫手諗下點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff196f5af715ecf038f367d7bbde479442afdba5","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T19:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9a1f9d96b818d0280f9a0f84caeb9e2db44f4e","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763fa7f00e3fed7fcc173621f9def091b6ebb778","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45841a24596b09c077a5d6d014c9f9a432734ae","tid":1904782,"uid":175346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"485cdf1c7d4bdfd03e3dc9f19f64f55e1a321901","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff5dd969076e43f8b42c0ff75e27ba5e06a218f","tid":1904782,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20